short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension for Redhawk faculty and staff at Westwood!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The W extension was designed for faculty and staff at Westwood High School to increase daily productivity. It is maintained by the school's Technology Learning Coach for the use and support of Westwood faculty an staff and requires no permissions to use it. It was created as a follow up to a previous extension and changed to include more items. It will not ever collect personal data as its purpose is strictly to support faculty and staff with daily planning.
